import React from 'react'
import {Link} from 'react-router-dom'
import {Container, Row, Col} from 'react-bootstrap'

const Category = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col className = "mb-0 my-3 " >

                            <Link className="btn btn-outline-primary my-3" to='/'>
                                카메라
                            </Link>

                            <Link className="btn btn-outline-primary my-3" to='/'>
                                헤드폰
                            </Link>

                            <Link className="btn btn-outline-primary my-3" to='/'>
                                휴대폰
                            </Link>
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        </>
    )
}

export default Category
